    Megatron looked Kitkat up and down. He grew very bored with her antics 
very quickly. "Both of you return to base now! we will settle it there. Here 
were in the open."
    Also, as insurence, he took out his tail gun and ignited the purple 
plasma that fuled it. If Kitkat decided to bail, she was going to do it in 
peices.

    Aracnia listened to Darkmouse and nodded. The Medical drone entered, 
saluted, and began to run its programmed diagnostic on her. Aracnia would 
later open the gym up for the mouse, it would allow her to warm her body up 
for a battle if needed.
